Class Constraint

java.lang.Object
org.apache.openjpa.jdbc.schema.Constraint
All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:

public abstract class Constraint extends Object
A table constraint. This class is closely aligned with the constraint information available from DatabaseMetaData.
